description:
On today’s show, Dr. Emily is bringing you part two of birth chart readings done by psychological astrologer Dr. Jen Freed & the two of them are helping callers navigate their sex & relationship lives.

Dr. Emily & Dr. Jen are talking to listeners to help them with their sex & relationship journeys based off of the exact time, place & date they were born. Some of the advice includes finding the courage to take the next steps in a relationship, how to get needs met with different sex drives, & putting words into actions in the bedroom. 

If you enjoyed both part one & part two of the show, please email feedback@sexwithemily.com & let us know! 


Follow Emily on all social: @sexwithemily

For more information on Dr. Jen Freed, click HERE.
